review:
A really good VN with a heart-touching story. Great art style, good selection of BGM and all the characters are likeable. For best experience go in this order:
Akane, who's really carefree and likes teasing, but actually kind and caring;
Inori, who's always really kind and caring, but even she can lose her temper sometimes;
Maika, as tsundere as it gets, but it only makes her cuter when she shows how kind and caring she actually is.
The only problem i had is the same as with the previous game which isn't that much of a problem it's just against my preferences, and that isthat there's only one choice to be made: choose which girl you want to be together.
All in all i can recommend both this and the previos LoveKami game as they're both really enjoyable.
